item.title: CVE-2018-10618|2024-08-05T07:46:46.120Z -- davolink -- dvw-3200n
item.description: Davolink DVW-3200N all version prior to Version 1.00.06. The device generates a weak password hash that is easily cracked, allowing a remote attacker to obtain the password for the device.
